"quantum gates do, we can use QiliSDK to build and simulate our own "
"quantum circuits. To create a quantum circuit in QiliSDK, we can use the "
":doc:`Circuit </modules/digital/digital_circuits>` class:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../tutorials/introductions/intro_circuits.rst:166
msgid ""
"This creates a quantum circuit with 2 qubits. We can then add gates to "
"our circuit:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../tutorials/introductions/intro_circuits.rst:175
msgid "And finally we should also add some measurements:"
msgstr ""

